headline.main: No. 3 UCLA Beats Washington State 77-68 for 9th Straight Win
headline.print_headline: No. 3 UCLA Beats Washington State 77-68 for 9th Straight Win

lead_paragraph: Sebastian Giovinco failed to convert a penalty as Toronto FC rang in the new season the same way they finished the old, playing out a scoreless draw on Saturday on the opening weekend of Major League Soccer (MLS).
